Package: ggwhiteboard
Type: Package
Title: Static and Animated Line, Shading, and Intersection Whiteboard Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Nick", family = "Huntington-Klein", role = c("aut","cre"), 
           email = "nhuntington-klein@fullerton.edu", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7352-3991"))
Description: This package provides a set of tools for creating ggplot-based
    graphs of the kind that might be drawn on a whiteboard,
    including lines, intersections between lines, shaded areas between lines,
    and so on. There is also support for animation of these graphs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    gganimate,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    scales
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0.9000
